&lt;li&gt;Bring a point of view on craft, process, and where the field is going, while staying current with new technologies and design trends&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please note: This role requires availability during Eastern Time Zone (EST) working hours.&lt;/p&gt;
